// Regression (PLT-227 / sei_legacy HTTP batch): a non-object batch element after a gated sei_* call
// must not cause full-body passthrough past enabled_legacy_sei_apis.
//
// Docker localnet omits sei_sign from enabled_legacy_sei_apis (see docker/localnode/config/app.toml).
// Correct behavior: slot 0 = legacy gate error (legacy_sei_deprecated); slot 1 = -32600 Invalid Request.
// Buggy behavior (early return to inner on per-element unmarshal error): sei_sign can reach the inner
// server and the response no longer contains legacy_sei_deprecated for that slot.
>> [{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":1,"method":"sei_sign","params":[]},42]
<<
@ expect_body_contains legacy_sei_deprecated
@ expect_body_contains Invalid Request
@ expect_body_contains -32600
